    "description": "TCG卡牌店模拟器是一款集换式卡牌商店模拟游戏，您可以通过出售卡牌补充包来赚钱，并发展您的卡牌商店业务。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070070/extras/9f8784083b81461a0fcc13442282745e.poster.avif?t=1762475483\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070070/extras/9f8784083b81461a0fcc13442282745e.webm?t=1762475483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070070/extras/9f8784083b81461a0fcc13442282745e.mp4?t=1762475483\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>管理您的商店：<br>设计您自己的TCG商店。整理货架和卡包，让顾客的购物体验更加顺畅轻松。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070070/extras/d5466d1f1cdfe40ab1203155d1cc72cc.poster.avif?t=1762475483\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070070/extras/d5466d1f1cdfe40ab1203155d1cc72cc.webm?t=1762475483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070070/extras/d5466d1f1cdfe40ab1203155d1cc72cc.mp4?t=1762475483\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>卡牌收藏：<br>亲自打开补充包并收集卡牌。寻找稀有卡牌并将其出售以赚取财富，或者将其收藏以完善您的卡牌收藏。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070070/extras/d05aad83593e0849a1f6904d4970e109.poster.avif?t=1762475483\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070070/extras/d05aad83593e0849a1f6904d4970e109.webm?t=1762475483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070070/extras/d05aad83593e0849a1f6904d4970e109.mp4?t=1762475483\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>主办游戏：<br>设置您的卡牌游戏格式和费用，邀请玩家在您的商店玩卡牌游戏。务必保持商店的清洁卫生，否则玩家可能会离开！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070070/extras/153eb4e293d32b366ea38984e8dec12c.poster.avif?t=1762475483\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070070/extras/153eb4e293d32b366ea38984e8dec12c.webm?t=1762475483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070070/extras/153eb4e293d32b366ea38984e8dec12c.mp4?t=1762475483\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>订购产品：<br>储备不同的补充包卡牌和卡牌游戏产品。密切关注流行趋势，并调整库存以满足顾客不断变化的需求。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070070/extras/5c4e1fbe14e8db61d596a6f0639f8ad6.poster.avif?t=1762475483\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070070/extras/5c4e1fbe14e8db61d596a6f0639f8ad6.webm?t=1762475483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070070/extras/5c4e1fbe14e8db61d596a6f0639f8ad6.mp4?t=1762475483\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>拓展您的业务：<br>赚取利润以再投资您的商店。扩大您的空间，解锁新的卡牌套装，并升级您的设施，以吸引更多顾客并增加收入。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070070/extras/30e3f795b4191ced9c17ada5ed1190ab.poster.avif?t=1762475483\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070070/extras/30e3f795b4191ced9c17ada5ed1190ab.webm?t=1762475483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.aka